      "message": "Hi Deepak — I\u0027ve completed the entity-type-specific D-Bus interface changes you asked about. I refactored PldmEntityReq from a concrete class inheriting Board to a template parameterized by the Item interface type (e.g. PldmEntityReq\u003ccpuserver\u003e for processors). A PldmEntityBase abstract base class provides the property setters via Decorator interfaces, and a createPldmEntity() factory function selects the correct template instantiation based on PLDM entity type. Mapped types are: Accelerator (GPU), Cpu, Dimm, Fan, PowerSupply, Chassis, Board (default).\n\nWould you prefer this folded into this change as PS3, or as a separate follow-up?",
